known_issues: Tiles not loading on browse page

existing_features.title: Debug and fix the issue preventing gift pack tiles from rendering on the catalog/browse page (CatalogPage.tsx). Investigate data fetching, filtering logic, and component rendering to identify why tiles are not displaying.
Verify that the useGiftPacks hook is correctly fetching gift pack data from the backend and that the filtered results are being passed to the ProductGrid component on the CatalogPage.

new_feature_requests.summary: Check if the backend main.mo actor is returning gift pack data correctly and that there are gift packs available in the backend storage to display on the browse page.
